            "creation_date": 1361983312,
            "body": "<p>If you are using EJB 3.1, you can create a <code>@Stateless<\/code> EJB, and mark one of the methods <code>@Asynchronous<\/code>. This is an out-of-the-box solution for Enterprise Java environment (<em>There<\/em> the external management of <code>Thread<\/code> resources are not recommended). <\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 15117471,
